// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2731 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b4956e48-3f5c-5075-a537-9143b0492327

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.10*")
